ActNational Security Act, 2017
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day After the Day on which this Order is Made as the Day on which Part 1.1 and Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing (1) the day after the day on which the Order is made as the day on which Part 1.1, other than section 49.2, of the NATIONAL SECURITY ACT, 2017, chapter 13 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COMES INTO FORCE; (2) the day after the day on which the Order is made as the day on which sections 94, 96, 97, 101, 102, 107 and 108, and the provisions enacted by them, as well as sections 110 and 111, of the Act, COME INTO FORCE; (3) the later of the day after the day on which the Order is made and the day after the day fixed under section 169 of the Act as the day on which section 101 COMES INTO FORCE; and (4) the day after the day on which the Order is made as the day on which section 128, subsection 129(1), sections 131, 134 and 135, subsections 137(2), (4), (5) and (7) and section 139 of that Act, COME INTO FORCE.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2019-0071 Publication Date: 2019-07-24
